data.description: A Stunning 4+1 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath Gem in Garfield Ridge. This charming raised ranch with a spacious addition boasts large bedrooms with vaulted ceilings, soundproof windows, and doors, newer roof and a 2.5-car garage.  The large primary bedroom features an en-suite bath and a walk-in closet. The entire home has been freshly painted and waiting for your finishing touches. With a generous yard, this home is perfect for families and outdoor enthusiasts. Schedule your viewing today, your dream home could be just around the corner!
